title: How I Met Your Mother - S09E23 S09E24 - Last Forever A Second Op
description:
CONTAINS SPOILERS! STOP READING IF YOU HAVEN'T WATCHED YET>



The finale of How I Met Your Mother was unforgivable. 

They ruined Barney and Robin. They took a beautiful, poignant relationship situation with Ted and his soul mate and shoehorned in some bullshit with Robin.

On and on. The finale was terrible.

I fixed it.

The divorce? Gone. The blue horn? Gone. 

It's still a little rough and I struggled with whether to leave the baby stuff in there with Barney, but it's implied now that Barney and Robin fix their shit and somehow, magically, have a baby. I thought it showed that Barney grew up one more little bit. I think it should feel like Robin is just a crazy work-a-holic.

Most importantly it now ends focused on Ted and his soul mate.
